Son House (SH) talks about his first wife and marriage (continued from
SR016
).

(continued from
SR017
) Son House is talking about Charlie Patton in Lula, Michigan. Patton had a Stella guitar. SH and Patton did not play together. SH talks about Patton's background, e.g., where he came from. SH talks about going to Grafton, Michigan with three other musicians to make recordings.

